description: Astounding 1770 Sqft Thomas Park Triplex Condominium. This Beauty features a Renovated Kitchen with Granite Countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances. High ceilings. Gleaming Hardwood floors. Exposed Brick. Huge windows that allow a ton of Sunlight. Laundry In-Unit. Private Rear Deck and Patio w/ yard. Pet Friendly Condo association. Minutes to Andrew Square MBTA. Moments to Carson Beach and Seconds to Shops, Restaurants and all that South Boston has to offer.
